               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184302270164"></xptr>
               <p>two pigeons in the shop window at five o'clock in the evening of the 7th of Feb.—I missed them when the policeman came about half-past five, and saw them on the pavement, about four or five doors from my house—an officer picked them up—they were mine.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430227-name-782" type="witnessName">
